WEBVTT

00:04:28.426 --> 00:04:31.895
we give too much authority to the wicked

00:04:31.919 --> 00:04:35.569
who steal funds
and beg God for forgiveness.

00:04:37.376 --> 00:04:39.441
Now for those of you
who are not religious,

00:04:39.465 --> 00:04:41.674
you also have to change
your mindsets about us.

00:04:42.449 --> 00:04:45.106
There are many of us who are hardworking,

00:04:45.130 --> 00:04:47.670
ethical and intellectual.

00:04:47.694 --> 00:04:48.945
It might surprise you.

00:04:48.969 --> 00:04:51.179
(Laughter)

00:04:51.203 --> 00:04:52.682
Now the second step

00:04:52.706 --> 00:04:56.223
is that we have to utilize
our resources and assets

00:04:56.247 --> 00:04:57.397
for social impact.

00:04:58.052 --> 00:04:59.336
In England,

00:04:59.360 --> 00:05:05.267
1,900 churches have been
shut down since 1969,